                                    h4.heading.heading_zilla.heading_zilla-xxxs What makes forms inaccessible?
                                    ol.links
                                        li.links__item
                                            p CAPTHCA. It's 100% inaccessible for disabled people, 100% inaccessible for ad blocker and VPN users and 100% annoying for anyone else.
                                            blockquote Imagine you buy yogurt and shop assistant asks you if you're robot
                                            p Why do we forgive such distrust of sites?
                                            p If you cannot live without making your users` life harder, please find CAPTCHA alternatives.
                                        li.links__item
                                            p Fields are not accessible via Tab. Label form controls properly and hardly ever change Tab order.
                                        li.links__item
                                            p Hidden Errors. Website's telling me I'm wrong and should redo work. Who obeys who? Provide polite notifications.
                                        li.links__item
                                            p Is it a checkbox or a bird? Default browser's fields appearance can not fit your website design. But don't forget they are the design standard. You can decorate it, but not to alter.
                                        li.links__item
                                            p Forms don't remember us.
                                            blockquote
                                                |
                                                    — How much is banana yogurt?
                                                    — 43
                                                    — and cherry?
                                                    — 48
                                                    — then banana one
                                                    — What is banana?
                                            p Why do we forgive sites for their forgetfulness?
                                            p The form should “remember” everything user put in it. Do not force the user to do all the work again after an error, reloading or accidentally closing the page.
                                        li.links__item
                                            p Uncertainty. If I check it, do I enable or disable it?
                                            p Action form controls labels — always a verb — and it must correspond to the action that will occur when a button is pressed, box is checked, etc.

